Interface ApplicationGatewayListener.UpdateDefinitionStages

  • Enclosing interface:
    ApplicationGatewayListener

    public static interface ApplicationGatewayListener.UpdateDefinitionStages
    Grouping of application gateway HTTP listener definition stages applicable as part of an application gateway update.
